## Bundle Contents

```
{{ bundle_name }}/
  MANIFEST.md                  -- this file
  manifest.json                -- machine-readable metadata
  health/
    health_summary.json        -- aggregate health status
    health_summary.txt         -- human-readable health report
  state/
    <hostname>/
      bgp_summary.json         -- BGP neighbour table
      interfaces.json          -- interface status and counters
      routes.json              -- IP route table / route summary
      running_config.txt       -- full running configuration
      logs.txt                 -- last 200 log lines
      version.json             -- platform version info
  drift/
    drift_summary.json         -- aggregate drift results
    drift_summary.txt          -- human-readable drift report
```
